5
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,530
And I can't even remember it. It's killing me.

6
00:01:34,270 --> 00:01:35,270
Ah.

7
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,200
Well...

8
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:39,590
We didn't do it.

9
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,120
Huh?

10
00:01:43,610 --> 00:01:45,340
We didn't go all the way.

11
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:51,690
You lied about that too?

12
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,660
I just asked you...

13
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:55,010
