14
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:58,380
You'd almost stripped me naked.

15
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:06,020
And then the moment I looked away,

16
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,050
you fell asleep.

17
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:12,060
It was pure torture.

18
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:16,170
But...

19
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:18,050
