20
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:20,060
Isn't it a good thing that nothing happened?

21
00:02:20,980 --> 00:02:22,330
That's not right, either.

22
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:25,680
Even though we had just met,

23
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,830
