29
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,580
I thought I might really be alone from now on.

30
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:43,070
So I was feeling pretty down.

31
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,530
It was right then...

32
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:48,690
