33
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:53,140
You should've had a friend take you home.

34
00:02:55,100 --> 00:02:57,530
You even cared about me, a total stranger.

35
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:59,320
You're such a good little brother.

36
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:02,620
There's no need to get over your brother complex.

37
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,970
Not at all!

38
00:03:12,290 --> 00:03:14,980
It was the first time someone's touch felt so comforting.

39
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:22,650
Since you're so bummed about it,

40
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,450
