41
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:28,390
You get hurt precisely because you trust people.

42
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,910
And while it's true I was upset,

43
00:03:31,510 --> 00:03:32,690
that's no reason to...

44
00:03:33,390 --> 00:03:35,220
There's no point in hurting the other person.

45
00:03:36,970 --> 00:03:39,510
To be able to forgive someone who betrayed you...

46
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:42,010
Since we chose to end it this way,

47
00:03:42,330 --> 00:03:44,370
if she doesn't end up happier than before,

48
00:03:44,370 --> 00:03:45,510
it would really bother me.

49
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:50,510
So people like that really do exist.

50
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,190
I thought to myself,

51
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:56,180
There are people out there, unlike my mom,
who can love someone gently.

52
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,080
You can be open and let me spoil you.

53
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:06,200
I want to feel these big, warm hands more often.

54
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:08,690
I felt it right then.

55
00:04:08,690 --> 00:04:10,070
With you, it would be okay.

56
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:14,820
So that's why you were so angry then.

57
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,260
Yeah.

58
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:21,250
But we've finally made it this far.

59
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:24,930
I'm sorry.

60
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,820
I'll never...

61
