62
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,490
I know.

63
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:39,140
Don't look at me like that.

64
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:44,110
I'm going to...

65
00:04:45,970 --> 00:04:47,240
I'm going to take in all of you.

66
00:04:49,290 --> 00:04:50,560
So I'll never forget again.

67
00:05:11,350 --> 00:05:12,450
Is that okay?

68
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,400
Wait.

69
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:16,650
