99
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:56,660
I don't know.

100
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,440
But...

101
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:02,460
I think he's doing his best to figure things out right now.

102
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,680
Even though you're already prepared...

103
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,580
