When faced with a future with no guarantees,

108
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:24,220
what can I do to make him feel secure?

109
00:08:26,770 --> 00:08:27,770
Brother...

110
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,780
Thank you, Shizuma.

111
00:08:37,310 --> 00:08:38,720
