115
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:57,120
to fill us in on everything.

116
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,520
And?

117
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,590
If you guys want to be together,

118
00:09:01,990 --> 00:09:05,500
