144
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,770
You'll feel reassured.

145
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:15,840
And you'll remember how much you love him.

146
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,960
It'll make you feel better.

147
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,580
Things that made me happy...

148
00:10:31,930 --> 00:10:32,930
huh?

149
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:43,290
Even though I've always...

150
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,530
avoided getting close to people,

151
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:54,360
before I knew it, Shizuma was by my side.

152
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:00,170
Morning.

153
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,370
Just having him look at me,

154
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:05,530
just touching each other,

155
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,790
could make me feel so content.

156
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:11,990
I never would have imagined.

157
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:16,390
Even though I was so happy,

158
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,900
I love you.

159
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:19,190
Minato.

160
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,810
I want to make you happy.

161
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:24,990
I won't let you regret it.

162
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,190
Choose me.

163
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,550
So, how are things?

164
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,160
Um...

165
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:50,870
Are things going well with that guy?

166
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,640
By the way, what's his name again?

167
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,240
Oh.

168
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,600
Minato.

169
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,760
Minato.

170
00:11:58,090 --> 00:11:59,090
Right.

171
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,580
I haven't properly introduced you guys yet.

172
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,850
No need. We're just...

173
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,740
As long as you're feeling better,

174
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:05,800
that's all that matters.

175
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,850
Yeah.

176
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:08,770
If you ever have any problems,

177
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,270
you can always talk to us.

178
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:13,100
Thanks.

179
00:12:14,310 --> 00:12:15,510
Once things settle down,

180
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:16,940
I'll introduce him to you guys properly.

181
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:17,980
Oh.

182
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,300
- Are you two dating?
- Hey, Yuka...

183
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:22,200
He already said that.

184
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,860
- Once things settle down...
- What's that supposed to mean?

185
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,280
You know.

186
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,950
Let me reply to a message.

187
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:43,900
(Minato: Where are you now?
Shizuma: Just got out of class. At the university cafe.)

188
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,200
(Minato: I see. Okay.)

189
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:52,800
(Minato: Then come over to my rooftop.)

190
00:12:55,130 --> 00:12:56,130
Sorry.

191
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,640
I'm going to see Minato.

192
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,170
Now? Seriously?

193
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:02,070
- See you tomorrow.
- Yeah.

194
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:07,710
Nice.

195
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:21,540
Sorry to keep you waiting.

196
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,100
It's beautiful.

197
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,380
Yeah.

198
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,480
This camera...

199
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:46,850
was a gift from my brother when I was a kid.

200
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:49,760
Oh, really?

201
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:52,080
It's old...

202
00:13:52,930 --> 00:13:54,740
but it's like a good luck charm to me.

203
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,800
You know...

204
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,020
I was looking at the photos from this camera again today.

205
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:05,840
Oh?

206
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:07,870
Shohei...

207
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:10,050
he told me whenever I'm anxious...

208
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:12,730
to think about happy memories.

209
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:15,700
That guy...

210
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:21,090
Thinking about my time with you...

211
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:25,280
my heart was just so full.

212
00:14:30,690 --> 00:14:32,340
And that's when I realized...

213
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:37,950
I've been lonely this whole time.

214
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,420
My mom always looked so stern...

215
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:48,050
but she was just lonely.

216
00:14:49,070 --> 00:14:50,960
I bet she wanted to cry, too.

217
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:58,620
Me...

218
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:01,900
I was so happy you were there for me.

219
00:15:05,050 --> 00:15:06,840
The way you're so serious all the time...

220
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,080
your terrible photography skills...

221
00:15:10,330 --> 00:15:12,020
even how cute you are when you're drunk...

222
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:12,870
I love everything about you.

223
00:15:21,610 --> 00:15:24,390
That's why I'll never... ever leave you.

224
00:15:26,210 --> 00:15:27,210
I'm going to get...

225
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:28,540
stronger.

226
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:34,630
So you better be by my side to watch me.

227
00:15:36,950 --> 00:15:37,950
I'll be watching.

228
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:40,530
I'll always be right here by your side.

229
00:15:44,220 --> 00:15:45,220
Okay.

230
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:03,140
- Hey, there's no way I'm losing!
- Ugh...

231
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:04,230
Isn't that triple points?

232
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:06,460
- Doesn't that mean I win?
- It's triple!

233
00:16:06,530 --> 00:16:08,030
Oh, welcome!

234
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:11,730
- Look who's here together!
- This is great!

235
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:14,060
Sorry for all the trouble.

236
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:14,530
Oh, stop.

237
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:16,220
Did you two come all this way
just to tell us that?

238
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:18,830
- What a stud.
- So cool.

239
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:22,270
All right, stop teasing them.

240
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,270
I had a feeling you two would show up.

241
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,040
I saved you the best seats in the house.

242
00:16:27,810 --> 00:16:29,790
Just for you two.

243
00:16:31,020 --> 00:16:32,050
Wow, that's so nice.

244
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,300
He said they're the best seats.

245
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:35,730
Mind if we join you?

246
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:38,120
I want to hear Minato's side of the story, too.

247
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:40,320
Huh?

248
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,520
Of course.

249
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:45,010
- Hey, no fair! I wanna listen too!
- What is it?

250
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:46,600
- Come on, sit down.
- Me too, me too!

251
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,880
Me too!

252
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:48,960
Come on, come on, come on.

253
00:16:49,530 --> 00:16:50,530
Have a seat.

254
00:16:51,980 --> 00:16:52,980
It's so lively in here.

255
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:56,600
- Yeah, this is really great.
- It really is.

256
00:16:56,660 --> 00:16:59,460
- We're all so happy for you guys.
- So happy, so happy.

257
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:05,950
- But really, I'm sorry for all the trouble.
- It's nothing.

258
00:17:05,950 --> 00:17:06,550
(Message from Tatsumi)

259
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:07,990
I didn't really do anything to help...

260
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:12,290
(Tatsumi: Take care of Shizuma for me.)

261
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:17,140
My world used to be just my brother.

262
00:17:18,870 --> 00:17:21,430
Somehow, it's become so much bigger.

263
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:27,000
- I don't think there's anything wrong with that.
- But I'm so sorry... It's all my fault...

264
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:30,420
Exactly.

265
00:17:33,170 --> 00:17:34,570
If the old me could see this now...

266
00:17:34,570 --> 00:17:35,700
he'd probably pass out from the shock.

267
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:56,870
I love you, Minato.

268
00:18:03,130 --> 00:18:04,350
I love you too.

269
00:18:06,530 --> 00:18:07,660
Ever since the day we first met...

270
00:18:07,660 --> 00:18:08,730
I've been in love with you.

271
00:18:25,460 --> 00:18:26,950
I'm all yours.

272
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:29,880
You better take good care of me.

273
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,460
You okay?

274
00:19:26,970 --> 00:19:28,170
