281
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,240
This.

282
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:00,500
I want this to be us.

283
00:20:01,710 --> 00:20:03,730
No way... Absolutely not.

284
00:20:03,770 --> 00:20:05,930
Old guys wearing matching heart sweaters?

285
00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:08,190
We'd be a laughingstock.

286
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:10,880
You think so?

287
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:13,500
By the time we get that old...

288
00:20:13,710 --> 00:20:15,750
it might not be so strange.

289
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:20,490
If I'm going to grow old with anyone...

290
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,140
I want it to be you.

291
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:26,670
Even so...

292
00:20:27,080 --> 00:20:29,040
I don't want to look like "that".

293
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,560
I know, I know.

294
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:34,690
It was just an example.

295
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:40,470
What are you doing?

296
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:44,540
As long as it's not the hearts...

297
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:46,630
I might consider it.

298
00:20:56,330 --> 00:20:58,870
- Mmm...
- I told you, you're jumping the gun.

299
00:21:04,190 --> 00:21:05,820
I'm not going to forget you just said that.

300
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:12,350
Growing old with me won't be easy, you know.

301
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:14,310
If you ever cheat on me...

302
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:16,290
I might just kill you and eat you.

303
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:21,290
The feeling's mutual.

304
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,440
But...

305
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:26,030
if I can, I want to grow old with you.

306
00:21:26,770 --> 00:21:27,770
And...

307
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:29,440
I want to wear matching heart sweaters...

308
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,710
in a field of cosmos flowers.

309
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,440
I'm telling you...

310
00:21:32,670 --> 00:21:34,380
no heart sweaters.

311
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:42,470
- It's too embarrassing. - What's the big deal?
- Then you can wear it by yourself.

312
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:43,820
No way.
